Token.Abstract: A credentials provider that uses AWS STS web identity federation.

Asynchronously returns a valid AWS credentials or an error object if it cannot retrieve valid credentials. It should cache valid credentials as much as possible and refresh them when they are invalid.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A valid AWS credentials or an error object describing the error.

Token.Abstract: Invalidates the cached temporary AWS credentials. If the credentials provider does not cache temporary credentials, this operation is a no-op.
